sagex.phoenix.fanart

Class LocalFanartSupport

  • java.lang.Object
    • sagex.phoenix.fanart.LocalFanartSupport
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IFanartSupport

    public class LocalFanartSupport
extends java.lang.Object
implements IFanartSupport
    Local Fanart Support implements the FanartAPI but only looks for Fanart, in the Local Directory. ie, backdrops, banners, etc reside in the same directory as the local file.
